</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_182" id="89v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hartung vom Eglofstein, pfleger czum Rotenberg
                    </ab>
